Let A = {1, 2} and B = {2, 3}. Find the following sets using the Cartesian product and intersection operation: 

1. (A × B) ∩ {(1,2), (2,3)}
2. {(1,2), (2,3)} ∩ (A × B)
3. (A ∩ B) × {3}
4. (A × {3}) ∩ (B × {3})
5. (A × B) ∩ ((A ∩ B) × {3})

